external_knowledge:
- "ships docked at the New York harbor" refers metaphorically to stocks traded at the New York Stock Exchange (NYSE).;
- "selling their treasures" is a metaphor for the closing stock prices. The treasures being sold are the stocks at their closing prices at the end of each trading day.;
- "throughout the year 2023" indicates the time frame from January 1, 2023, to December 31, 2023.

sql:
SELECT company_name, AVG(market_cap) AS avg_market_cap
FROM stock_symbols
GROUP BY company_name;
